OL,3,CSenior politician calls for
OL,4,Cindependent inquiry into health
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FGuernsey's Deputy Chief Minister is
OL,8,Fcalling for an independent inquiry
OL,9,Finto historic complaints against the
OL,10,Fisland's Medical Specialist Group
OL,11,F(MSG).
OL,13,FDeputy Gavin St Pier says he will
OL,14,F"continue to press for systemic and
OL,15,Fcultural change" within the health
OL,16,Fservice and "will not stop trying to
OL,17,Frepresent the interests" of families
OL,18,Fwho have raised concerns with him.
