OL,7,FHe has submitted questions to Deputy
OL,8,FGeorge Oswald, the President of
OL,9,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,10,FCommittee, for him to respond to
OL,11,Fduring next week's States' sitting.
OL,13,FIn it, Deputy St Pier outlines an
OL,14,Femail he says was sent by a concerned
OL,15,Ffamily to the island's Chief Executive
OL,16,Fand Head of the Public Service - which
OL,17,Fhe is sharing with their permission.
