OL,7,FHe says it states that "most families
OL,8,Ffeel renewed terror about speaking
OL,9,Fout" following recent events, which
OL,10,Fsaw Deputy St Pier and his wife
OL,11,Farrested for harassment - they were
OL,12,Flater released without charge and
OL,13,FGuernsey Police says investigations
OL,14,Fare ongoing.
