OL,7,FDeputy St Pier asks: "Does the
OL,8,FPresident agree that urgent action is
OL,9,Frequired to build public confidence
OL,10,Fand faith in States regulatory,
OL,11,Fgovernance and complaints processes
OL,12,Fand to remove any fear or repercussion
OL,13,Ffor those engaging with them?"
OL,15,FHe also poses the question about what
OL,16,Fsteps are being taken to review the
OL,17,Fcomplaint processes of the MSG and
OL,18,FHealth and Social Care.
