OL,7,FThe States' independent Commissioner
OL,8,Ffor Standards, Dr Melissa McCullough,
OL,9,Fpreviously stated that independent
OL,10,Freviews "have consistently found no
OL,11,Fwrongdoing related to Dr Bohin's
OL,12,Fclinical judgement or her actions" and
OL,13,Fthe allegations are "extremely serious
OL,14,Fand unfounded".
OL,16,FThe Commissioner resigned from her
OL,17,Fposition after politicians voted
OL,18,Fagainst her recommendation that Deputy
OL,19,FSt Pier should be suspended for his
OL,20,Factions.
