OL,4,Cindependent inquiry into health
OL,5,Ccomplaints
OL,7,FDr Steve Evans, Chair of the Medical
OL,8,FSpecialist Group, has previously
OL,9,Fstated that Deputy St Pier must be
OL,10,Fsanctioned for "the long and unfair
OL,11,Fcampaign waged against Dr Bohin".
OL,13,FHe added that criticism of their
OL,14,Fcomplaint process is "unfair".
OL,16,FDr Evans explained: "We have a joint
OL,17,Fcomplaint policy with HSC (Health and
OL,18,FSocial Care) and MSG, there's a robust
OL,19,Fprocess with deadlines, and there's a
OL,20,Fright of appeal if people are unhappy
OL,21,Fwith the outcome.
