OL,7,F"I think in the cases where we've
OL,8,Freceived complaints, they've been
OL,9,Finvestigated thoroughly, appropriately
OL,10,Fand fairly.
OL,12,F"I think the other thing you have to
OL,13,Fconsider is that if a patient
OL,14,Fapproaches a deputy or a third party
OL,15,For the media, they can share as many
OL,16,Fdetails as they want to, whereas as
OL,17,Fprofessionals we are duty-bound by a
OL,18,Fcode of confidentiality."
