OL,7,FIn response to Deputy St Pier's calls
OL,8,Ffor an independent inquiry, an MSG
OL,9,Fspokesperson says: "We take all
OL,10,Fconcerns raised by patients and
OL,11,Ffamilies seriously, and we are
OL,12,Fcommitted to learning from every
OL,13,Fexperience to improve the care we
OL,14,Fprovide.
OL,16,F"We welcome any opportunity to
OL,17,Fdemonstrate our commitment to
OL,18,Ftransparency and accountability in
OL,19,Fserving our patients."
